{"tid":1758119,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美民調顯示大部分受訪者贊成美國表態支持香港示威者","createTime":"2019-11-27T01:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T03:05:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab5d6a0af6eab5706e0c798ec8cd3a54a280167","tid":1758119,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:07:47.000Z","msg":"美國一項民意調查發現，68%受訪者贊成美國表態支持香港爭取民主示威者，而不必理會可能會觸怒中國，只有14%受訪者支持中國的立場。<br />\n<br />\n國會參眾兩院上周在幾乎無人反對的情況下，通過《香港人權與民主法案》。總統特朗普上星期表示，雖然支持香港爭取民主，但亦支持國家主席習近平。<br />\n<br />\n由朗奴列根基金會贊助的民調發現，大部分國民不認同特朗普的對華立場。69%受訪者表示，如果解放軍在香港鎮壓示威，他們會支持美國向中國實施制裁，59%受訪者支持美國向香港示威者提供安全或其他援助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494642-20191127.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494642-20191127.htm&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRCYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=d8f533fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494642-20191127.htm&h=97742c2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494642-20191127.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c0100a2123d07df0f062b232fa2da536f0c09ee1","tid":1758119,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"68%高過總統當選普選票數比例<br />\n可被視為理所當然的廣泛民意"},{"pid":"555a191d0adfcfa3afc2215b713f7a169db9a7d4","tid":1758119,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"所以話，侵唔得無簽香港人權法案，這是民意。除非他唔想連任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da82acd2a4cf08eb0cbd4bdaafd3109175e0199f","tid":1758119,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555a191d0adfcfa3afc2215b713f7a169db9a7d4","tid":1758119,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"所以話，侵唔得無簽香港人權法案，這是民意。除非他唔想連任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,